#: dist/converse-no-dependencies.js:95743
msgid ""
"Moderators are privileged users who can change the roles of other users "
"(except those with admin or owner affiliations."
msgstr ""
"主持人是特权用户，可以更改其他用户（具有管理员或所有者从属关系的用户除外）的"
"角色。"

#: dist/converse-no-dependencies.js:95745
